ng bestinclass secure payment services that deliver incremental value and revenue to our customers and their merchants we work collaboratively with our clients to develop solutions that help them meet today’s business challenges and tomorrow’s opportunities our team of skilled personnel across the world share one vision — to serve as a trusted partner dedicated to helping our clients and their merchants grow their business one platform our single currency neutral payment platform the keystone of our business allows us and our clients to enter new markets and deliver new services quickly we nimbly deliver stateoftheart solutions to our clients in a fraction of the time effort and cost it might take for them to develop or enhance their own systems once connected to our platform in one country our customers and their merchants can use the same interfaces and pointofsale devices in all other countries in which we operate planet payment we are committed to delivering innovative payment services that fulfill the promise of helping our customers and their merchants improve their business efficiencies and sell more goods and services about usour company leadership team senior management news center legal  privacy terms  conditions privacy  security about cookies careers employment opportunities media center collateral library video library   related press planet payment and aci worldwide launch unionpay international’s secureplus  muxi and planet payment announce agreement to offer multicurrency processing on their pos terminal solutions  planet payment announces first quarter  results  network international and planet payment announce multiyear contract extension merchant milestone  planet payment  delivers innovative payment processing solutions search for one partner one platform planet payment planet payment delivers innovative payment processing solutions that solve many of the challenges facing today’s global electronic payments industry we deliver our payment process