retail restaurant and hospitality environments we also provide payment services for ecommerce and mail and telephone order merchants our pointof sale and ecommerce services help merchants sell more goods and services to consumers and  together with our atm services are integrated within the international payment card transaction process enabling our acquiring customers to process and reconcile payment transactions in multiple currencies geographies and channels we are a registered third party processor with the major card associations and operate in accordance with industry standards including the payment card industry or pci security council’s data security standards nasdaq plpm     day high  na day low  na volume  na  pm et on  delayed at least  minutes  mo  mo  yr events  presentations  at  pm et planet payment inc first quarter  financial results  at  pm et planet payment inc fourth quarter  financial results view all events  presentations » facebook google linkedin twitter email rss   press releases kcb bank and planet payment announce launch of pay in your currency®  planet payment and aci worldwide launch unionpay internationals secureplus  muxi and planet payment announce agreement to offer multicurrency processing on their pos terminal   planet payment announces first quarter  results  locations  planet payment search for locations home   locations corporate headquarters  long beach boulevard long beach new york  united states of america t     f     infousplanetpaymentcom americas atlanta  great oaks way suite  alpharetta ga  united states of america t     delaware one corporate commons west commons boulevard suite  new castle de  united states of america t     f     bermuda th floor washington mall phase ii  church street hamilton bermuda hm t     canada  yonge st suite  toronto on mcx t     infocanadaplanetpaymentcom mexico av paseo de la reforma no  piso  col juarez delegacion cuauhtemoc cp  ciudad de mexico t     asiapacific singapore  eu tong sen stree